          "commentType": "SUBUNIT",
          "texts": [
            {
              "value": "Component of a cohesin-like complex composed of ScpA, ScpB and the Smc homodimer, in which ScpA and ScpB bind to the head domain of Smc. The presence of the three proteins is required for the association of the complex with DNA"
